words: Din ko raat kahegi toh main raat kahoon

Le lunga teri saari balaayein meri jaan
Teri aayi, main marjaavan, zindadi naam tere kar jaavaan

Kya wo mohabbat, jiska hisaab lag jaaye

Ho sawaal koi bhi, tu jawaab lage
Bachpan ki kahani, tu koi khwaab lage
